      <vspace*|1fn><with|font-series|<quote|bold>|math-font-series|<quote|bold>|3<space|2spc>Semantic Entailment 语义蕴含 ><datoms|<macro|x|<repeat|<arg|x>|<with|font-series|medium|<with|font-size|1|<space|0.05fn>.<space|0.05fn>>>>>|<htab|5mm>><no-break><pageref|auto-14><vspace|0.5fn>

