      <with|par-left|<quote|1tab>|3.2<space|2spc>Satisfiability of a set of formulas 一组公式的满足<datoms|<macro|x|<repeat|<arg|x>|<with|font-series|medium|<with|font-size|1|<space|0.05fn>.<space|0.05fn>>>>>|<htab|5mm>><no-break><pageref|auto-16>>

